title: 820-00165 smc_reset_l is 0V
message: good day guys , this board is making me go crazy, SMC_RESET is 0V , but when I remove R5110 it goes high , when I put it back its low, I replaced it, but no difference , I tried with the SMC as well as R7100 to rule out a faulty U7100, and even R5100 replaced , all with no changes , please where do I go from here ?
